es. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 5 animals_matter_a_lot" link="https://viewer.diagrams.net/?lightbox=1&amp;nav=1&amp;chrome=0#Uhttps%3A%2F%2Fraw.githubusercontent.com%2Fmorganrivers%2Ftrain_to_crazy_town%2Fmain%2Fdiagram%2Ftrain_tree__w1_2_3_5.drawio" id="w1_2_3_5"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f5d3b8;strokeColor=#cc7a33;fontColor=#5a300e;dashed=1;dashPattern=8 4;strokeWidth=3;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1139" y="478" width="200" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Suffering-focused&lt;br&gt;ethics&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+6]&lt;br&gt;→ The Humane League&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx9Vm1z4jYQ%2Fis7TDuFDCHG5KVHhw8kcV6mXC%2BTo73phAwR9hqrJ0seSY7j5vLfu7IhQIB%2BwnhXj57dfR7Jr40IY5YLe6EibPQbR0cwGAxgrBmXYBWEmv1b0kMhYZL7XvcYCqVF9MyxgKI79ae96Sk0jVUZnLbc0okkiKExeZpZriSECSH1wYOMaRUmnAkH1P3kQxdipqesYOU0yVMmzTLgA5M8ZcJMjUqxSJhdRnoQ5zbXuFgwTZm1qKcFt8k04iZUubRczpfpp2DyOEZNr6axCnODUUUvYGECbMWRG2BwV9qEnmMuEKj2VdgcgXUcWBSZNmikhnGJBpSuwDQeUmksRWLCDb23CdZV%2F2KIrgwrjN8gVGmmjGP3nkBrZYSESK%2B4qdCMZTJiQkmElCYiOvD03vDg%2BclRdcvxJcPQ0sJnJnIEFVcIq9l0KrBzNBZmeQm528YtNLheWB%2FGhHXjeokwQjbPsV54HfwR3A%2FHwSXMSpijRM0sdrJyqQGMuN3o0AEF2yCVrXm4JhJShXXJNVEFpEHQD3UYXfeVnlN7Mk1z1iXMaIuYh5ye23AeXH25D6h8zUSFUCCfJ26u1AyhnCoT%2FlQPTai5VJq0Ap%2B8n%2BHiFppKU6mHKj5M2Vxym0cI51%2FGwUWL%2BBiVZ79zGyYoL5ko71D%2FaSIYwOtEAmSoMoE3KDKM3iNexztxG3qdE5dToBAzJCbXND0HUad43TrH67qkSoWoYxbanIlzJr%2F%2FVQ3Jpfb27HSwA%2FoAml043AfXmsi3iZxHG4U4Lt7xgoznTyRL462E3qIizye6jKdbCctqfKrZJmIj3u34Lnp8Rt0sss2Q73kudnZMJCay4CKa5XOzmXNa5%2FzqVzlMiBi3S%2FDfW07eKJT6mFHFHYK30FjwUFwOR38De0btXJGR2n967K9LLdqQoeXpwqkrmYWKgiRClPaDm2g5%2B3CiQZZb49TMrRNWqJyLB%2FDg5vsK1Hfsw6QxUiFJ08kOvte6mzTaUETv5fQhRSabO4XZIgWQYuCtvQl6zZ%2BxNpUod8Otq%2BL%2FUL6R5sAd3VSS5raE5vDzVWs35oaSHOg25PD2MxzBxQIrkFZjRicc5tokPNsDu66%2FfVy3TqndWBtarbG6J92z3vEW4NeEDp4MqH66ghDutPqH2rlnNusyr1C34L6R1OnOMIRhoJnUTDM6fElNEZo9Hd02yG704Wh0FVzuad8HA9VVk8d3DAcMi9EN%2Bb42FdzTdcB0mOzht%2BW9Fb1H5ztNR5G7zgYw4sZ2NJL5DDarP0Zpe142a1%2B04fXHyw946azt8daiA2zm7qcBLIAevMeFncc7b7jxze3XlSf7UH0YcOr4bHnNkds5sTDkyLVLk3ZwGeu7T2Tj7T%2FaNQkY" id="w1_2_3_6"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#f2ccc0;strokeColor=#c96a4a;fontColor=#5a2410;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1014" y="717" width="236" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Meat-eater problem&lt;br&gt;(saved humans eat animals)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+6+7]&lt;br&gt;→ The Humane League&lt;br&gt;(Michael Dickens, Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + suffering_focused + meat_eater_problem&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The meat-eater problem: a dollar of human global health also buys decades of that person&#x27;s meat consumption, and factory farming it causes suffering the animal circle now counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Vm1v4kgM%2FisWutNBD2jCS2k58YG29EXL3lZd9lanUqVD4pC5TWaimUlTrtv%2Fvp4EChT4gAix57H9%2BLGH10qAIcticyEDrPQrx8cwGAxgohgXYCT4iv2%2FoIdcwDRrOW4Hcqni4JljDrnrtby2d%2BL1oKqNTKFXs4engkCGWmdJargU4EeE1QcHUqakH3EWWyj3rAUuhEx5LGcLL8oSJvTK0AImeMJi7WmZYB4xs7K0IcxMpnB5wEuYMai8nJvIC7j2ZSYMF%2FOV%2BwnoLAxR0SsvlH6mMViZepAgMx596Hyq5CzGpEh9xPwI2Dp%2FroHB3cJE9BzyGIGYWZv1MRibHwsCXQeFRCcXqEGqAkxhg8pmCVIUrum9ibBk5A9NpQi%2FwPgLfJmkUtvM3x3orAiQEOkV1wWaNkwELJYCIaF%2BxU14em%2FH6PnJpmqP40uKvqGDzyzOEGRYIKw71yzAzlEbmGULyGwYe1DjZmF9mBDWjeUZYYxsnmF58Hr09%2Bh%2BOBldwmwBcxSoiMNmulgpBANuthg6ImMdhDRlHpZEQiqwLrmiVAGpSfRFDKNlX6o50ZMq0oBawIxChNzn9FyH89HVl%2FsRla9YXCDkyOeR7TmREUur2Yg%2FlU2L5VxIRTqCM%2Bd3uLiFqlRUakOGjYTNBTdZgHD%2BZTK6qFE%2BWmbpJ278CMUlixd3qL7pAAbwOhUAKco0xhuMUwzeLU7T6dqATrNrfXKM4xlSJtfUPQtRujhu6eO41qlQKKqQ%2BSZj8TkTP%2F4pmmRd2wciHe2BPoKqC41DcLWpeJuKebBViM3F6SyTcVpTwZJwx6G9rMhpUbqMJzsOq2paVLOJ4i2722xZa6dHbObptqnlONbW61ASU5HzOJhlc73tc1L6nLYKHxbHIe6W0HqnnGYjl%2FKjR2G3CM5SY6OH%2FHI4%2FhfYMyo7FSmp%2FbfH%2FqbUgi0ZGp4sJ3UtM1%2BSkUSIwnyYJjrOPmw7SDOjrZq5scLypZ3iATzY%2Fr4C8Y59mFbG0idpWtnBj1J300od8uC9nL5dUaK6V5g1UgApBv6EaqPb7PVOTzrYcLo1eKtvR7nmz1hOWbzYj78pk03YQi%2Bu4571zvbDfidVgl38VLTiZgHV4eer2v4gW1qzUdYxXMfpnu4JMbz9DMdwscQeCaMwpZ2ImdIRTw%2BE2VTsTjGn7knbPd2NtLPo9oNvyb0Ed7tur93ZAfwa0e5KgQiiGw7hTsn%2FqAEH2rs5KQXqDtx3mha6djRhaKhGZaYp7W8SZID6AOW7M7YffTgeX40uD%2FD5YQbLqmlN7OkWaBaiVcF9OZdwTzcKU350IL%2Bd8V2n92hHV9E2szfiAMZcm6ZCml%2BN1eKHlsqcL6rlaNXh9efLT3hpbsR4q9EOnNkrbgBLoAfncbkRJnsvycnN7df1WPeh%2BN%2FBifHZ6qakhcEpC01DvXHvUgTrsRl9KipvvwD0dB%2Bh" id="w1_2_3_6_7"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#eec2a8;strokeColor